  "subject": "Add hpa controller framework",
  "commit_message": "Add hpa controller framework\n\nEnable gRPC communication\nbetween controllers and\norchestrator by adding .proto\nand stubs to controller pkg.\n\nAdd hpa_placement code/build tools\nin seperate application space.\n\nUpdate go.mod and go.sum for\nochestrator.\n\nAdd mongo, etcd, k8sclient pkgs\nto orchestrator.\n\nIssue-ID: MULTICLOUD-729\nSigned-off-by: Marcus G K Williams <marcus.williams@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I8b9b932d4186fd1d259a39962e4043edd3d0f63e\n",
